# AttendX — Phase 1 Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Phase 1 scaffold — a complete **backend + frontend foundation** with auth flow ready for end-to-end testing once Firebase is configured.

---

## Decisions Made

| Decision | Choice | Why |
|----------|--------|-----|
| Design palette | Slate + coral, dark mode default | Per user preference + PRD §4 |
| Tailwind version | **v4** (CSS-first @theme config) | User requested latest |
| Email service | **Resend** | Modern API, generous free tier, simple Python SDK |
| Monorepo | `attendx-backend/` + `attendx-frontend/` inside `attendX/` | Per user preference |

